-- Euro Pares Loss Against Dollar on Optimism for Greek Bailout Compromise
-- B y   K e n n e t h   P r i n g l e
-- 2012-02-16T15:44:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-16/euro-pares-loss-against-dollar-on-optimism-for-greek-bailout-compromise.html
The euro pared its loss against the
dollar on optimism policy makers will strike an agreement that
will allow  Greece  to win approval a rescue package.  European governments are considering cutting  interest rates 
on emergency loans to Greece and using contributions from the
 European Central Bank  to plug a new financing gap in the second
bailout program for  Athens , two people familiar with the
discussions said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Pringle at 
 kpringle3@bloomberg.net  